  <brief_title>Bioavailability Study of K0706 in Healthy Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open Label, Four Period, Four Sequence, Single Dose, Crossover Study to Evaluate Relative Bioavailability of K0706 24 mg Tablet Formulation Relative to 24 mg Capsule Formulation Under Fasted Conditions and to Evaluate the Food Effect for Tablet Formulation in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
